OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Don't forget millions have
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto work on Coronation'     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, With the Coronation approaching, there 
OL,6, has been a call to "spare a thought"   
OL,7, for millions who will have to carry on 
OL,8, working through the holiday weekend.   
OL,10,FTrade union leader Paul Nowak hailed   
OL,11,Fthose in jobs such as shops, transport 
OL,12,Fand hospitality who will be working, as
OL,13,Fwell as emergency services.            
OL,15,F"Their labour will allow others to make
OL,16,Fthe most of the celebration," said TUC 
OL,17,Fgeneral secretary Mr Nowak.            
OL,19,FAbout a fifth of workers regularly work
OL,20,Fon bank holidays, say the trade unions.
